{"tid":1132574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Hkcc Dse雙修唔識揀","createTime":"2019-04-30T11:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T11:53:04.000Z","uid":248097,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"699ed77f2bb588b95924bba80fbb55dc37816988","tid":1132574,"uid":248097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:49:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟18年dse21分英文2左  之後唸住一邊讀hkcc一邊retake dse 3科 （3:7咁溫）邊邊考得好就揀邊邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家hkcc sem1 4.3gpa sem2預計應該都穩陣過4<br />\n但考完dse對過下網上答案都幾有信心升到24/25分，不過英文就唔係100%肯定有3（大概8成信心左右）<br />\n最on9係hkcc6月頭交學費 dse 7月10先放榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽聞延遲交學費多數都係grant個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴打有冇辦法/經驗可以拖到dse放榜先交學費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋如果真係只可以揀一邊應該dse定hkcc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46e407b215412602df1cd6c69313d64c8afdc5b","tid":1132574,"uid":79869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"重考DSE有幾難？ 僅8%達入大學最低門檻 邊科「翻身率」最高？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/140514/%E9%87%8D%E8%80%83dse%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BE%E9%9B%A3-%E5%83%858-%E9%81%94%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB-%E9%82%8A%E7%A7%91-%E7%BF%BB%E8%BA%AB%E7%8E%87-%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F140514%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%2580%2583dse%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E9%259B%25A3-%25E5%2583%25858-%25E9%2581%2594%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%258E%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25AA%25BB-%25E9%2582%258A%25E7%25A7%2591-%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E7%258E%2587-%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598&d=jZUVzsr%2BlXwf2hbAbvJm1ZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=691317a3\" data-auto-link t